        {
            "title": "彭博新聞午間分享 你會想知道的五件事",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推進AI</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">阿里巴巴計畫將其旗艦網絡購物、旅遊服務接入千問應用，邁出打造一站式人工智能平台的重大一步。摩根資產管理預計中國科技領域將迎來「更多DeepSeek時刻」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">繼續降溫</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">時隔十年，中國再次啟用提高融資保證金比例這一措施為熱情高漲的股市降溫，A股周四繼續回落，近期暴漲的人工智能應用板塊在有多家公司提示交易風險後跌幅居前。摩根士丹利認為管理層此舉旨在推動「慢牛」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">干預風險</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">日圓兌美元匯率從18個月低點反彈，日本財務大臣片山皋月發出干預警告並強調不排除任何手段。不過，對沖基金押注日圓可能跌至165關口之後才會引發干預行動。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-9446d7e5-a793-3bf1-940e-f2fbbd1c1202-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"> </p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">按兵不動</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">韓國央行決定維持利率不變，並在政策聲明中刪除潛在降息的措辭，當局擔憂韓元貶值和樓市過熱。美國財長貝森特罕見發聲支持韓元，稱該貨幣貶值幅度過大，與韓國經濟基本面不符。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">最後衝刺</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">華盛頓與台北之間持續數月的經貿談判正進入最後階段。台方談判團隊已經啟程赴美進行第六輪磋商，台灣政府預計雙方有望在本輪磋商後宣布達成的經貿共識。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"> </p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%BD%AD%E5%8D%9A%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E5%8D%88%E9%96%93%E5%88%86%E4%BA%AB-%E4%BD%A0%E6%9C%83%E6%83%B3%E7%9F%A5%E9%81%93%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%94%E4%BB%B6%E4%BA%8B-041420658.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-15 12:50:46",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "阿里巴巴將讓淘寶等APP接入千問 邁出打造一站式AI平台的重大一步",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:阿里巴巴;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/阿里巴巴\">阿里巴巴</a>集團計畫將其旗艦網絡購物、旅遊服務接入旗下人工智能(AI)應用程式，朝著將千問打造成消費者的一站式AI平台之目標邁出了迄今為止的最大一步。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這一中國互聯網零售領頭羊打算從周四開始，讓淘寶、支付寶、飛豬以及高德地圖接入千問App。阿里巴巴在聲明中稱，其設想是最終幫助千問的1億用戶借力AI，通過單一平台完成購物、酒店機票預定及支付。這種新整合的功能目前已在中國開始公開測試。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這項雄心勃勃的計畫，凸顯了從亞馬遜到Meta Platforms Inc.的各種公司正在如何探索智能體AI，即用AI幫助人們完成實際任務的工具。像阿里巴巴和騰訊之類的公司已然運營著有數百種服務的「超級app」，被認為在該領域具有先發優勢。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-e6f64ff2-c0a2-31b8-a37c-68e880ddb33b-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">阿里巴巴旗下還有流媒體服務以及中國最大外賣平台之一，於11月推出千問，大力進軍面向消費者的AI服務領域。該公司計畫通過逐步整合阿里系各項服務，將千問打造為全能型個人助手。阿里巴巴還推出了僅限受邀用戶使用的「任務助理」功能，可以執行更複雜的任務，例如為用戶致電餐廳或開發網絡應用。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">阿里巴巴尋求用這一舉措來回應全球對於AI盈利潛力的擔憂。鑒於未來對AI服務的需求仍存在不確定性，投資者尤其擔心流入用輝達晶片支撐起來的數據中心的全球海量資金。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/5GvTjCcTpiHvcaLIADM2Rg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/8cc22e84cd66b31521a852cdf6d9a8be\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">阿里巴巴將千問與淘寶連接起來，凸顯出其雄心之大。淘寶是阿里巴巴在數十年前推出的電商服務，而且今天仍在中國占據主流地位。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">阿里巴巴高管周四將演示新的千問功能的使用方式。他們計畫向用戶展示從本地門店點奶茶、在淘寶上購物和買單，以及確認餐廳或酒店預訂等操作的詳細步驟。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Alibaba Takes Major Step to Link Taobao Shopping to Main AI App</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Claire Che.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">(新增自第四段起的內容)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%98%BF%E9%87%8C%E5%B7%B4%E5%B7%B4%E5%B0%87%E8%AE%93%E6%B7%98%E5%AF%B6%E7%AD%89app%E6%8E%A5%E5%85%A5%E5%8D%83%E5%95%8F-%E9%82%81%E5%87%BA%E6%89%93%E9%80%A0-%E7%AB%99%E5%BC%8Fai%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0%E7%9A%84%E9%87%8D%E5%A4%A7-%E6%AD%A5-030723125.html",
