        {
            "title": "台積電淨利潤超出預期 再度凸顯人工智能需求旺盛",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Bloomberg, company filings\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"642\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/FxzQDORD2wZCJMxmoQSimA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MjtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/4688af4607236d420aaf1d937f096449\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Bloomberg, company filings</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 台積電業績超出預期，利潤成長強勁，印證了美國晶片設計商對人工智能硬體需求的樂觀預測。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這家全球最大的晶片代工企業周四公佈業績，截至12月31日的季度淨利潤為5,057億元台幣（約合160億美元），分析師平均預估成長25%，達到4,670億元台幣。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">台積電是亞洲市值最高的公司，也是人工智能熱潮中半導體行業最受關注的風向球。該公司業績表現強勁，季度營收超出預期達331億美元，助力全年營收首次突破1000億美元。儘管市場對當前支出可持續性仍有擔憂，但台積電與主要客戶輝達一樣，對人工智能需求推動長期成長表達了高度信心。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-828170f4-a725-35e8-8571-41b5c0cc7e14-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"642\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/DTrNgIfKWXm0b6TMFsG9Sg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MjtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/8414b181ccdb1e0298033d6e6fd8f8da\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題TSMC Profit Beats Estimates in Fresh Sign of AI Demand Strength</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Cindy Wang、Ville Heiskanen、Gao Yuan、Jessica Sui、Henry Ren.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8F%B0%E7%A9%8D%E9%9B%BB%E6%B7%A8%E5%88%A9%E6%BD%A4%E8%B6%85%E5%87%BA%E9%A0%90%E6%9C%9F-%E5%86%8D%E5%BA%A6%E5%87%B8%E9%A1%AF%E4%BA%BA%E5%B7%A5%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82%E6%97%BA%E7%9B%9B-061305212.html",
