            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"中國據悉尋求就對委內瑞拉的數百億美元貸款獲得保障\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"537\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/HiC7zAyFe71qTAfj2XIWAQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUzNztjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-01/e08c59a0-f1be-11f0-bfe1-172091450ae4\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">中國據悉尋求就對委內瑞拉的數百億美元貸款獲得保障</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
